c: 2
v: 54
t: "And remember Moses said to his people: \"O my people! Ye have indeed wronged yourselves by your worship of the calf: So turn (in repentance) to your Maker, and slay yourselves (the wrong-doers); that will be better for you in the sight of your Maker.\" Then He turned towards you (in forgiveness): For He is Oft- Returning, Most Merciful"